Incredible superhero strength.

Trouvé la force
De quelques courses,
De préparer
Le déjeuner
Pour le fiston,
Pour qui j'ai pris
Du chocolat 
Et des bonbons.
La #depression,
C'est quand on lutte
Chaque minute
Pour faire le bon(d).
#poesie

World Statistics claims that
Life span has increased.
Yet
Why are my friends already getting ready to leave?
They would rather trade their life
for a ticket to the unknown.
Than survive this unbearable semester
for all I know.
#poetry #academicpressure #depression #suicide
